<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pre-Application | GracefuLiving</title>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/pre-app.css">
</head>

<body class="pre-app">
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>GracefuLiving Application</h1>
        <p id="hero-description">
          This short application will help me learn more about you and your unique goals so I can determine<br>
          whether my services are the right fit to support your journey. Your responses will remain <em>confidential</em><br>
          and will help me understand how I can best <em>guide</em>, <em>support</em>, and <em>empower</em> you toward lasting balance and well-being.
        </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="body">

    <!--Pre application Screening questions-->
    <form id="pre-app-screening-form">

      <!--Question 1-->
      <fieldset>
        <legend> Are you currently experiencing burnout? <span class="required"> *</span></legend>
        <label>
          <input type="radio" name="burnout" value="yes">
          Yes
        </label>
        <label>
          <input type="radio" name="burnout" value="no">
          No
        </label>
      </fieldset>

      <!--Question 2 (only if Q1 == yes)-->
      <fieldset id="q2-fieldset" class="hidden">
        <legend>
          Are you currently experiencing any of the following?<span class="required"> *</span>
        </legend>

        <ul class="symptoms-list">
          <li>
            <label>
              <input type="checkbox" name="symptoms" value="decreased_sleep">
              Decreased sleep
            </label>
          </li>
          <li>
            <label>
              <input type="checkbox" name="symptoms" value="fatigue">
              Body and mind fatigue, even after a day off
            </label>
          </li>
          <li>
            <label>
              <input type="checkbox" name="symptoms" value="no_time_for_self">
              Difficulty making time for yourself (there’s always something else to do first)
            </label>
          </li>
          <li>
            <label>
              <input type="checkbox" name="symptoms" value="difficulty_saying_no">
              Difficulty saying “no” without feeling guilty or getting pushback
            </label>
          </li>
          <li>
            <label>
              <input type="checkbox" name="symptoms" value="carrying_pain">
              Feeling the weight of carrying everyone else’s (and your own) pain
            </label>
          </li>
          <li>
            <label>
              <input type="checkbox" name="symptoms" value="none" id="symptoms-none">
              None of the above
            </label>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </fieldset>

      <!--Question 3-->
      <fieldset id="q3-fieldset" class="hidden">
        <legend> Are you a healthcare worker?<span class="required"> *</span></legend>
        <label>
          <input type="radio" name="healthcare" value="yes">
          Yes
        </label>
        <label>
          <input type="radio" name="healthcare" value="no">
          No
        </label>
      </fieldset>
      
      <button type="submit" class="btn-next">See My Next Step</button>
    </form>

    <!--Ending 1: Go to application-->
    <div id="ending-1" class="ending" style="display:none;">
      <p>
        Thank you so much for your interest. Based on your responses, it looks like you may benefit from personalized
        support right now.
      </p>
      <p>
        Please complete the following brief questionnaire to schedule your appointment with Shante Kumar at your convenience.
      </p>
      <a href="/application" class="btn-next">Continue to Application</a>
    </div>

    <!--Ending 2: Non Healthcare Worker PDF-->
    <div id="ending-2" class="ending" style="display:none;">
      <p>
        Thank you so much for your interest. Due to the responses received, it seems the following practices would be
        of most benefit to you at this time.
      </p>
      <p>
        Many blessings on your journey. <br>
        <strong>Ciao for now,</strong><br>
        Shante Kumar
      </p>
      <a href="/pdfs/exercise1.pdf" class="btn-next" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Download Your Energy Reset Practices
      </a>
    </div>

    <!--Ending 3: Healthcare worker PDF-->
    <div id="ending-3" class="ending" style="display:none;">
      <p>
        Thank you so much for your interest. Due to the responses received, it seems the following practices would be
        of most benefit to you at this time.
      </p>
      <p>
        Many blessings on your journey. <br>
        <strong>Ciao for now,</strong><br>
        Shante Kumar
      </p>
      <a href="/pdfs/exercise2.pdf" class="btn-next" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Download Your Energy Reset Practices 
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
  <script src="/js/pre-app.js"></script>

</body>
</html>